Title: Evaluation Day
Plot: While Grissom and Catherine investigate the case of a human head that is found in the trunk of a car, Sara and Nick have a case of a body in the desert that's missing it's head. Warrick looks into a murder in a juvenile detention facility.
GuestStars: John Beasley, Ingo Neuhaus, Robb Derringer, Keri Lynn Pratt, Skip O'Brien, Joseph Patrick Kelly, Rhonda Farr, Darren Kennedy, Lee Cherry, Chet Grissom, Samuel L. Jones, Shonda Farr, Fred E. Ellis, Shirley Jordan
